1.0.1.name: wordpress/feed-layout
1.0.1.description:
Feed Layout lets to modify the feed contents adding headers, footers, copyright notices.

You can add a copyright notice to every post, a link in the bottom like a "continue reading", link to specila contents your reader can access only subscribing the feed, ads form ads servers like Tradedoubler, Zanox and so on.

Read more at Feed Layout official page.
